{
  "description": "I met Sanjay through a mutual friend (Elisa), and since knowing him I've been extremely drawn to his unique, progressive takes on everything from finance to business, AI and loads more.\n\nSanjay hosts a weekly podcast with Elisa called 'New Wave' - a must-watch for me to get my fix of tech topics through a human/approachable lens. Food for thought and would wholeheartedly recommend!"
}

{
  "description": "Known AL a while through Pudgy Penguins and he supported me in my early days of streaming. He's honest, kind and a great person within the ecosystem and beyond. \n\nA genuine human being (and penguin)."
}

{
  "description": "Abschud is a legend in the Abstract world. Had the pleasure of speaking with him personally, super smart and genuinely great person. His reputation comes from his words and actions\n\nIt’s hard to imagine Abstract without Abschud, he brings real value to shaping the community"
}

{
  "description": "KangBokSoon has been very supportive of me.  Every interaction we have is always pleasant.  KangBokSoon even has given me lots of support by having him and his friends join my Telegram channel."
}

{
  "description": "One of the strongest members of the Abstract community, very friendly and super engaging. Flockinho has always been one of the strong voices in the Abstract community, well respected across many communities and in CT. We are both members of the Pudgy community, and only positive things are said about Flockinho. Super happy to have him and to move the narrative forward together. A true gem, an awesome friend, and a free spirit. Well known, well respected, and definitely a certified Giga Chad.",
  "source": "Ethos Everywhere Wallet",
  "version": "1.0",
  "client": "web"
}

{"description":"I had the pleasure of meeting Becca in Dubai this year for Token 2049. She was one of the kindest and nicest people to come up to me and involve me in the activities.

I was able to connect with her on a friendly level and realize what a hard-working woman she is. She is remarkable and has made so much impact in Web3, not only through her job at AP, but also in the wider Pudgy Penguin Ecosystem.

It's been a joy to watch her live her dreams, achieve her goals, and now being part of the team."}

{
  "description": "I’ve met Eleni through one’s friend GC, Eleni is a funny and good human being (though she missed the jokes sometimes), while she also creates organic content instead of using AI or copy pasted posts. Plus I recently have learned that she’s a writer"
}

{
  "description": "One of best Angle and Abstract Giga Chad, also one of best streamer and content creator in Abstract community about Game, eco, etc \nI love the positive energy she shared always to everyone"
}

{
  "description": "Met him in abstract community, he’s one of the pillars of the entire Abstract community. The way he consistently puts out meaningful art, sharp insights, and pure value for the ecosystem, it lifts everyone around him."
}

{
  "description": "Was lucky enough to meet N3XT through Elisa's GC. Love how he blends IRL content with sharp insights and alpha. Proper down to earth guy. Only place I don't want to meet him is in-game (because he's a pro)"
}

{
  "description": "I don't know how she does it all at once - but everything I see Marianne put her mind to she excels in. Lucky to have met her through Abstract and take great pleasure following her journey. She is SUCH a hard worker and someone everyone in the space should look up to."
}

{
  "description": "I was onboarded to Claynosaurz through Andrew and recently discovered his spaces & podcasts. A unique mind that shares a lot of insight whilst remaining down to earth and personable. Trusted figure in the space."
}

{
  "description": "My Greek sister and wonderful friend. Lucky to have met Nancy through Abstract and watch her excel at everything she has put her mind to. She's doing such a good job on Spaces & streams and always has time to talk. Not only great content, but a truly lovely person too."
}

{
  "description": "Zorin is one of those people you can have the funniest conversations with and also excels at what he does. He's absolutely nailed his personal brand and has worked alongside some of the top teams in web3. He's kind and patient and I LOVE watching him on streams."
}

{
  "description": "Becca isone of the best people in pudgy penguin community. Still remember when I first bought my Lil, she was the person who approached me to help me with everything I needed. I love her posts and her help to all huddle"
}

{
  "description": "leeland is a good friend I made while being part of the Abs Gigachad community  an incredible place filled with kind people who share the same passion and mindset. Everyone is united toward growing something bigger together, and that sense of community is truly amazing."
}
